channel.title: My new RS program coded in C++
channel.description:
Finally I'm done creating my Runescape stealer. It's 100% FUD, and it's coded in C++. In the video you can see how to build the stub using the builder. If you don't know what this is, don't ask me. You need a little knowledge to set it up, it's using a php script to upload the data, instead of smtp (that way there's no passwords stored in the binary file)
Go full screen + HD to see clearly how it works.
*
